14:36','2015-11-20 09:14:36','','003 (3)','','inherit','open','closed','','003-3','','','2015-11-20 17:14:36','2015-11-20 09:14:36','',272,'http://wnworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/003-3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(279,1,'2015-12-06 18:18:44','2015-12-06 10:18:44','<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">一、移动端的需要注意的事项</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> 1.手机端要触发&quot;data-&quot;属相触发事件注意事项</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在苹果手机，通过data-的方式来绑定事件,奇葩的事情来了：例如\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"brush:jscript;toolbar:false;\">\r\n&lt;i class=&quot;gift_icon&quot; data-roler=&#39;myprize&#39;&gt;单击弹出来&lt;/i&gt;\r\n&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;\r\n	$(document).on(&quot;click&quot;, &#39;[data-roler=\"myprize\"]&#39;, function() { alert(&quot;弹出来！&quot;) });\r\n&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n<textarea class=\"dp-runcodetextarea\" id=\"runcodetextarea1\" rows=\"7\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n	&lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;title&gt;&lt;/title&gt;\r\n	&lt;script src=&quot;http://libs.baidu.com/jquery/2.0.0/jquery.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;\r\n		.demo-cursor{cursor: pointer;display: block; padding: 10px;background: #f60}\r\n		.demo-nocursor{display: block; padding: 10px;background: #5e5e5e}\r\n	&lt;/style&gt;\r\n	&lt;br/&gt;\r\n	&lt;br/&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;button data-roler=&#39;myprize&#39;&gt;点击验证是否弹出(button按钮)&lt;/button&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;br/&gt;\r\n	&lt;br/&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;i class=&quot;demo-cursor&quot; data-roler=&#39;myprize&#39;&gt;点击验证是否弹出(i标签设置cursor: pointer)&lt;/i&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;br/&gt;\r\n		&lt;br/&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;i class=&quot;demo-nocursor&quot; data-roler=&#39;myprize&#39;&gt;点击验证是否弹出(i标签未设置cursor: pointer)&lt;/i&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;br/&gt;\r\n		&lt;br/&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;demo-cursor&quot; data-roler=&#39;myprize&#39;&gt;点击验证是否弹出(div元素设置cursor: pointer)&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;br/&gt;\r\n		&lt;br/&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;div class=&quot;demo-nocursor&quot; data-roler=&#39;myprize&#39;&gt;点击验证是否弹出(div元素未设置cursor: pointer)&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n		&lt;br/&gt;\r\n		&lt;br/&gt;\r\n	&lt;div&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; data-roler=&#39;myprize&#39;&gt;点击验证是否弹出(button按钮)&lt;/a&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;\r\n	$(document).on(&quot;click&quot;, &#39;[data-roler=&quot;myprize&quot;]&#39;, function(event) { event.preventDefault();alert(&quot;弹出来！&quot;) });\r\n&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;\r\n</textarea>\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"dp-exampleBtn dp-exampleBtn-l\">\r\n	<a class=\"wn-btn wn-btn-success\" data-roler=\"runcode\" data-textareaid=\"runcodetextarea1\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\">测试(在iphone手机端打开)</a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我们发现button和a元素完全支持的，可是遇到其他的元素比如i，div等，事件的绑定就会失效！！！解决的方式\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"brush:css;\">\r\n.class{\r\n    cursor：pointer,\r\n}</pre>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> 2.iPhone 手机上对于电话号码的处理问题</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在苹果手机,对于类似电话号码的数字会显示为拨号的超链接，而且会在停留一小段的时间后变成白色，简直是奇葩，处理的方式是让其不被显示为拨号链接：\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"brush:xml;toolbar:false;\">\r\n&lt;meta name=&quot;format-detection&quot; content=&quot;telephone=no&quot;/&gt;</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> 3.button按钮在安卓和苹果手机上的表现差异</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在苹果和安卓的手机上，不同的设备，浏览器的对于button元素的按钮的渲染其实是不一样的，看下图(左ios设备，右是安卓)：\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n	<a href=\"http://wnworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/002.png\"><img alt=\"002\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437\" height=\"120\" src=\"http://wnworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/002.png\" width=\"320\" /></a><a href=\"http://wnworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/001.png\"><img alt=\"001\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-436\" height=\"121\" src=\"http://wnworld.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/001.png\" width=\"318\" /></a>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这个时候我们往往想要通过设置：display: inline-block;&nbsp;padding: 15px 18px;来让按钮达到统一的宽高，但是这样子竟然有bug，点击查看<strong><u><a href=\"http://wnworld.com/MySummary/button/button.html\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\">demo</span></a></u></strong>(在苹果手机端打开)，padding失效！！竟然失效，怎么处理？经测试发现：需要改按钮添加背景色或者边框就可以有效：\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"brush:css;\">\r\n/**\r\n * btn1在ios中对于button元素是失效的\r\n */\r\n.btn1{\r\n	display: inline-block;\r\n		padding: 15px 18px;\r\n		\r\n}\r\n/**\r\n * btn2在ios中对于button元素是有效的\r\n * background 和 border 只要设置其中一个就可以\r\n * bootstrap 在设置按钮的时候也是有默认的btn-default\r\n */\r\n.btn2{\r\n	padding: 15px 18px;\r\n	display: inline-block;\r\n	background:#f60;\r\n	border:1px solid #000;\r\n}</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n','移动端网站需要注意的细节','','publish','open','open','','%e7%a7%bb%e5%8a%a8%e7%ab%af%e7%bd%91%e7%ab%99%e9%9c%80%e8%a6%81%e6%b3%a8%e6%84%8f%e7%9a%84%e7%bb%86%e8%8a%82','','','2017-02-09 17:59:36','2017-02-09 09:59:36','',0,'http://wnworld.com/?p=279',0,'post','',1),(283,1,'2015-11-28 10:47:18','2015-11-28 02:47:18','<p>\r\n	[phpcode file=''scriptstyle'']\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	[phpcode file=''header'']\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"header-font\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wn-container 